            "title": "日股以近全日高位收市 單日漲0.85%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">日股低開高走，全日維持反覆向上趨勢。日經平均指數以接近全日高位收市，報53333點，升448點或0.85%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15615918-%e6%97%a5%e8%82%a1%e4%bb%a5%e8%bf%91%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e9%ab%98%e4%bd%8d%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82-%e5%96%ae%e6%97%a5%e6%bc%b20-85",
